        "description": "Norfolk Climate Change Partnership - The Broads Authority is a member of the NCCP. This is a partnership of local government in Norfolk, which identifies joint projects to work on. The partnership delivered a \\'Net Zero Communities Pathfinder\\' project, which is working with local people in 8 small communities to design a roadmap to net-zero. This includes two communities in the Broads. \\nhttps://www.norfolkclimatechange.co.uk/norfolk-netzero-communities/. This project completed in 2025. \\n\\nCurrent work is focused on developing a Local Area Energy Plan and Water Resources Plan, in partnership with the authorities in Suffolk. \\n\\n",
