        "comment": "CCR Energy Vision and Strategy sets out targets for the region to contribute to the National (Wales) decarbonisation targets. All 10 Local Authorities are working to contribute to carbon reduction targets to 2035 as set out in the strategy across their regions. In addition, Local Authorities and now CCR CJC are working towards Welsh Government ambition for the public sector to be Carbon Neutral 2030 target for their own operations (covering Scope 1, 2 and 3). CCR will be establishing targets and transition pathway to Net Zero 2030 covering their own operations in 2025/26."
