        "description": "The council is part of the Environmental Sustainability Theme Working Group of the Universities Partnership which includes the two city Universities (https://universitiespartnership.org/home-universities-partnership/environmental-sustainability/). The council has collaborated with the two universities in the city on various projects, including energy audits for businesses, carbon literacy training delivery to local schools and guidance on climate action planning for community groups. Both universities are represented on the Leicester Climate Emergency Partnership, as well as Leicester College. The council is also a signatory of a Civic Agreement with local universities, which includes co-operation on sustainability issues. ",
        "otherEntities": "Education sector|Residents/community groups|NGO and associations"
