        "description": "The council has led in the establishment of Leicester's Climate Emergency Partnership, which has brought together a range of civil society and statutory organisations and businesses to develop and deliver collaborative projects and funding bids to drive the city's carbon neutral ambition. The production of a carbon neutral roadmap study by the city council helps to inform the work programme for the partnership. A communications sub-group of the partnership board has been set up to maximise the impact and reach of climate communications and marketing opportunities.",
