        "description": "The council has a dedicated Sustainable Schools team, delivering a wide variety of engagement actions with schools in the city, including those not under local authority control. This includes a number of education programmes to connect with students on environmental issues. The team also works with the schools themselves, helping them to monitor and address their environmental impacts, seek funding for relevant projects and introduce low carbon technologies. ",
