        "description": "York Green Business Forum operates to bring together Yorks businesses to receive talks and workshops from leaders in various aspects of climate change and carbon reduction. York Green Business Forum has included events on the following topics: Energy, Waste, Transport, How to be a Standout Brand. York Green Business Forum aims to help businesses transition towards Net Zero. ",
