        "description": "Currently working with NGO's and local authorities across the EU e.g. France, Rumania, Italy and the Netherlands on the exchange of experience and futher development of 'Landed Kitchens'' local food growing projects linked to community kitchens providing prepared food for families that need it A Horizon 20:20 bid recently submitted. \\n\\nSharing experience with other Cities on the development of adaptation and resilience initiatives to reduce the impact of extreme weather events on the City and the use of Greenspace such as the innovative extensive programme in Paris. Working with the Scottish local authorities on Just Transition development in Scotland unlike England the Scottish Climate Change Act made a specific reference to a just transition Coventry has ties with Glasgow and Edinburgh with this regards.",
