        "focusAreas": null,
        "description": "Vulnerable Groups included the Row 8 activities as well. \\n\\nWorking with the Integrated Care Board and NHS for the introduction of 'Air Alert' for patients with COPD and respiratory illnesses, where air quality warning will be issued on days where monitoring is picking up high levels of gaseous emissions in the atmosphere in order to issue warnings and guidance as what to do on that day for those at risk.\\n\\nWorking with the Behavioural Economics team at Warwick University and the ICB on the development of co-ordinating pharmacies in promoting the uptake of ECOFLEX energy efficiency grants for people with specific health conditions using the repeat prescriptions service.",
        "otherEntities": "Regional government|Energy|Health Care"
