        "comment": "Dundee City Council engages with the Scottish Government through its funded Adaptation Scotland programme, delivered by Verture, to support the establishment of Climate Ready Tayside. This regional adaptation partnership brings together local authorities (Angus, Dundee, Perth & Kinross), alongside public bodies and community organisations, to coordinate adaptation planning across the Tayside region. The Council contributes staff time, resources, and governance input to this partnership, ensuring local priorities are aligned with the Scottish Government's ambition for regional adaptation partnerships to be in place across Scotland by 2029."
