        "description": "The Dundee Climate Leadership Group provides active leadership on Dundee's Net-Zero challenge, leveraging expertise from across the city which includes the public and private sector to engage and inspire collective ownership and a shared commitment to tackling climate change. For more information about the group and the partners, view via the link here: https://www.sustainabledundee.co.uk/about-us/dundee-climate-leadership-group",
