        "description": "ECC has partnered with Hertfordshire CC and Suffolk CC to ensure residents have continued access to local recycling and reuse facilities for bulky waste types that cannot be collected at the kerbside. By putting in place reciprocal arrangements which enable residents to use facilities in neighbouring administrative areas, we are seeking to make reuse and recycling as simple as possible for residents and reduce miles travelled.",
