        "mechanisms": "Collaborative initiative",
        "focusAreas": "Transport (Mobility)|Emissions reduction",
        "description": "ECC works with the Essex and South Suffolk Community Rail Partnership to promote a shift to rail travel and to involve the community. Includes projects that promote wilding and biodiversity that will have a small beneficial impact on carbon emissions. https://esscrp.org.uk/environment/",
        "otherEntities": "Residents/community groups"
