        "focusAreas": "Waste|Emissions reduction",
        "description": "ECC has extensively engaged with Central Government as a Circular Economy Pathfinder, aiding the development of a national Circular Economy strategy. ECC has also, through both formal consultative exercises and informal engagement, helped shape the direction of legislation for extended producer responsibility , deposit return schemes, emissions trading and simpler recycling - all of which are focussed on the delivery of a more circular economy and greater carbon efficiency in the use of resources.",
