        "description": "With the public's input, Hartlepool Borough Council made a climate pledge in 2021. Hartlepool Borough Council is committed to taking a leading role and working with everyone across the Borough to act now on the causes and impacts of climate change. We committed to take action to reduce the Council'sgreenhouse gas emissions and limit the climate crisis.",
