      "quantifiesEquity": null,
      "equityEvidence": "Through our Managment Plan, alongside climate-related issues we have a theme which is 'Inclusive Forest', with a vision that: People within reach of the New Forest, of all backgrounds, abilities and socio-economic groups, value the National Park as an important part of their lives and seek to care for it. We are in the process of commissioning an update climate risk assessment and action plan which will act as a key driver for action not just for the climate response theme, but for all aspects of our Management Plan.\\n\\nOur Lottery Community Fund project Youth for Climate and Nature will be evaluated in part by assessing and understanding the wider impacts of this specific group of actions undertaken by partners across the landscape. This learning will inform future project and investment planning."
