        "comment": "North Tyneside Council works closely with the North East Combined Authority (NECA). The Mayor for North Tyneside sits on NECA's cabinet and is Cabinet Member for Home to the Green Energy Revolution. This portfolio oversees Energy, Net Zero, and Environment and Coast, giving NTC the opportunity to inform climate action on a regional basis."
