        "comment": "North Yorkshire Council works in partnership with the White Rose Forest to increase woodland and forestry cover where appropriate in North Yorkshire in order to maximise benefit to residents and the environment through increasing flood alleviation, carbon sequestration, air quality, wildlife and creating new economic opportunities. https://whiteroseforest.org/about"
