        "focusAreas": "Resilience|Agriculture|Ecosystem restoration|Natural environment|Adaptation",
        "description": "PDNPA works in collaboration with national government to support the delivery of environmental land management subsidy schemes. At present this is primarily undertaken through the Farming in Protected Landscapes project, which provides advice and support for farmers to access funding and then deliver outcomes for nature and climate friendly farming. \\n\\nSince the last reporting period, PDNPA also delivered a test and trial project for national government to support the development of new environmental land management subsidies. The results of this trial have been reported back to the Department for Environment, Food and Rural Affairs.",
