        "comment": "PKC's finalised Climate Change Strategy and Action Plan was developed following an engagement process that ran from October 2020 through to January 2021. This included an online survey which consisted of five thematic questionnaires, as well as, ten online sessions that facilitated a discussion between PKC and the attendees. The scope of the engagement was to identify the challenges, opportunities and priorities for climate action across the Council area in order to create a net zero vision that is fair for all. The engagement feedback was therefore considered in the development of the action plan."
