        "description": "During 2024 we established a climate hub as a web-based resource for local groups. This is a one-stop shop for resources and case studies of projects being delivered by local community groups and climate networks.\\n\\nhttps://www.southdowns.gov.uk/climate-action-hub/\\n\\nhttps://www.southdowns.gov.uk/?s=knowledge+hub\\n\\n",
