        "comment": "As part of the region's shared Net Zero goal -WM2041- the WMCA has a role in supporting the local authorities in the region to meet this goal. The regular 'Net Zero Directors Meeting' is made up of Directors (related to climate change/environment) from the seven local authorities and the monthly meetings provide the opportunity to share information, collaborate and generally facilitate capacity building. The WMCA has a convening, influencing and supporting role, so it is critical to work with the local authorities in the region and this is done throughout all the workstreams managed by the Environment Team and Energy Capital. "
