        "comment": "As well as the Net Zero Directors meeting, the WMCA chairs and convenes a total of 11 groups that bring together a diverse range of officers from the seven constituent authorities, to deliver the key areas of our programmes. The local authority groups all focus on a specific area and are an opportunity to support collaboration, and in some cases, deliver particular projects. The groups are as follows: Retrofit Steering Group, Net Zero Infrastructure Delivery Panel, Local Area Energy Planning - Coordinating Group, Local Area Energy Planning- Heat sub-group, Net Zero Neighbourhood Working Group, Natural Capital Officers Group, Environment Behaviour Change Group, Climate Adaptation Group, Circular Economy Group, Air Quality Framework Delivery Group, Local Investment in Natural Capital Working Groups. These groups facilitate information sharing, support regional collaboration and support capacity building. "
