      "opportunitiesIdentified": "The many co-benefits for actions are outlined within the action plan itself. They include reducing pollution, generating fuel savings, enhancing biodiversity, and support economic growth, to mention a few. In addition wider opportunities for additional benefits can be assessed through a specific tool at the project proposal stage.",
